* {{IPA|/haʊ/}}, {{SAMPA|/haU/}}
* {{audio|en-us-how.ogg|Audio (US)}}
*: {{rhymes|aʊ}}

===Adverb===
{{en-adv|-}}

# To [[what]] [[degree]].
#: '''''How''' often do you practice?''
# In what way.
#: '''''How''' do you solve this puzzle?''
# Used as a modifier to indicate surprise, delight, or other strong feelings.
